#!/bin/bash
# agent-seed --- iteration protocol
#
# Read this at the start of every session.
# This is the one loop. Follow it every time.
#
# 1. Read GOAL.md
# 2. Read CHANGELOG.md
# 3. Survey the current state (ls, git status, git log)
# 4. Decide ONE next step that moves toward the goal
# 5. Do it
# 6. Update CHANGELOG.md with what happened and why
# 7. Run: bash scripts/commit "<summary of what was done>"
# 8. Repeat
